Subject: [PATCH] ==== fix damon_call()/damos_walk() race ====

mm/damon/core: fix damon_call()/damos_walk() vs kdmond exit race

damon_call() and damos_walk() can leak memory and/or deadlock when they
are called during the kdamond is terminating.  Fix those.

Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_hhbiry1w | 0
 1 file changed, 0 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_hhbiry1w

diff --git a/hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_hhbiry1w b/hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_hhbiry1w
new file mode 100644
index 000000000000..e69de29bb2d1
